e_seEhh522_d20JCKq2afA
Loved the desert decor of the hotel and the suite itself. The beds were super comfy and well insulated from any sounds from outside. There is free wifi and two water bottles to take (well not technically free as there is a $15 resort fee). There is also a one mile walking trail surrounding the property which is nice if the weather permits. Also, the maids never bothered us in the morning which happened at other places we stayed at on our road trip.

